<html>
<head>
    <title>Panel de Optimizacion</title>
    <HTA:APPLICATION
        ID="OptimizerPanel"
        APPLICATIONNAME="Panel de Optimizacion"
        BORDER="thin"
        BORDERSTYLE="normal"
        CAPTION="yes"
        MAXIMIZEBUTTON="no"
        MINIMIZEBUTTON="yes"
        SHOWINTASKBAR="yes"
        SINGLEINSTANCE="yes"
        SYSMENU="yes"
        WINDOWSTATE="normal"
        SCROLL="auto"
    />
    <style>
        * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif;
            background: #0d0d1a;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 480px;
        }
        h1 { text-align:center; font-size:20px; margin-bottom:2px; color:#e94560; }
        .subtitle { text-align:center; color:#555; margin-bottom:10px; font-size:12px; }
        .rambar-wrap { background:#1a1a2e; border:1px solid #2a2a4a; border-radius:8px; padding:10px 14px; margin-bottom:14px; }
        .rambar-label { font-size:12px; color:#aaa; margin-bottom:5px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; }
        .rambar-track { background:#111; border-radius:4px; height:10px; overflow:hidden; }
        .rambar-fill { height:100%; border-radius:4px; background:linear-gradient(90deg,#06d6a0,#1b9aaa); }
        .section { color:#555; font-size:10px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; margin:14px 0 6px 2px; }
        .btn { display:block; width:100%; padding:13px 16px; margin:7px 0; border:none; border-radius:9px; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; text-align:left; color:#fff; }
        .btn:active { opacity:0.82; }
        .btn-streaming { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#9146FF,#6441a5); }
        .btn-gaming    { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1b9aaa,#06d6a0); }
        .btn-restore   { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c0392b,#8e1a10); }
        .btn-clean     { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#e67e22,#a04000); }
        .btn-update    { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2980b9,#1a5276); }
        .btn-power     { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#8e44ad,#5b2c6f); }
        .btn-dns       { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#27ae60,#1a5e35); }
        .btn-context   { background:#1a1a2e; color:#888; border:1px solid #2a2a4a; }
        .desc { font-size:10px; font-weight:400; opacity:0.7; margin-top:3px; }
        .row { display:flex; gap:7px; margin:7px 0; }
        .row .btn { margin:0; flex:1; font-size:13px; padding:11px 14px; }
        .status { margin-top:14px; padding:12px 14px; border-radius:8px; background:#1a1a2e; border:1px solid #2a2a4a; font-size:12px; min-height:50px; line-height:1.7; }
        .status-label { color:#e94560; font-weight:bold; margin-bottom:3px; font-size:11px; }
        #overlay { display:none; position:fixed; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.88); padding:16px; overflow-y:auto; z-index:99; }
        .modal { background:#12122a; border-radius:10px; padding:18px; border:1px solid #333; }
        .modal h2 { color:#e94560; margin-bottom:10px; font-size:15px; }
        .modal textarea { width:100%; height:240px; background:#0a0a18; color:#ccc; border:1px solid #333; border-radius:6px; padding:10px; font-size:11px; font-family:Consolas,monospace; resize:none; }
        .modal-footer { margin-top:10px; display:flex; gap:8px; }
        .mbtn { padding:8px 20px; border:none; border-radius:6px; cursor:pointer; font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:#fff; }
        .mbtn-copy { background:#3a3a5a; }
        .mbtn-close { background:#e94560; }
    </style>

    <script language="VBScript">

        Dim WshShell, FSO
        Set WshShell = CreateObject("WScript.Shell")
        Set FSO = CreateObject("Scripting.FileSystemObject")
        Dim highPerfActive : highPerfActive = False

        Sub RunPS(code)
            WshShell.Run "powershell -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command " & Chr(34) & code & Chr(34), 0, True
        End Sub

        Sub SetStatus(msg)
            document.getElementById("statusText").innerHTML = msg
        End Sub

        Sub RefreshRAM()
            Dim wmi, col, obj, total, free, usedPct
            Set wmi = GetObject("winmgmts:\\.\root\cimv2")
            Set col = wmi.ExecQuery("SELECT TotalVisibleMemorySize,FreePhysicalMemory FROM Win32_OperatingSystem")
            For Each obj In col
                total = CDbl(obj.TotalVisibleMemorySize)
                free  = CDbl(obj.FreePhysicalMemory)
            Next
            Dim usedGB, totalGB, freeGB
            totalGB = FormatNumber(total/1048576, 1)
            freeGB  = FormatNumber(free/1048576, 1)
            usedGB  = FormatNumber((total-free)/1048576, 1)
            usedPct = CInt(((total-free)/total)*100)
            document.getElementById("ramText").innerHTML = "RAM libre: <b>" & freeGB & " GB</b> &nbsp;|&nbsp; Usada: " & usedGB & " / " & totalGB & " GB"
            document.getElementById("ramFill").style.width = usedPct & "%"
            If usedPct > 80 Then
                document.getElementById("ramFill").style.background = "linear-gradient(90deg,#e74c3c,#c0392b)"
            ElseIf usedPct > 60 Then
                document.getElementById("ramFill").style.background = "linear-gradient(90deg,#e67e22,#d35400)"
            Else
                document.getElementById("ramFill").style.background = "linear-gradient(90deg,#06d6a0,#1b9aaa)"
            End If
        End Sub

        Sub OptimizeStreaming()
            SetStatus "Optimizando para STREAMING..."
            RunPS "$p=@('Dropbox','setup','UpdateDriver','LogiAiPromptBuilder','CCleaner','SearchApp','RemoteMouse','msedgewebview2','OneDrive','Spotify','Discord','Steam','EpicGamesLauncher','warp');foreach($n in $p){Stop-Process -Name $n -Force -EA SilentlyContinue};Stop-Service 'CCleaner_service' -Force -EA SilentlyContinue;[GC]::Collect()"
            RefreshRAM
            SetStatus "Streaming listo -- Cerrado: Dropbox, Discord, Steam, Warp, OneDrive, Spotify<br>Arranca OBS y Twitch."
        End Sub

        Sub OptimizeGaming()
            SetStatus "Optimizando para GAMING..."
            RunPS "$p=@('Dropbox','setup','UpdateDriver','LogiAiPromptBuilder','CCleaner','SearchApp','RemoteMouse','msedgewebview2','OneDrive','Spotify','warp','chrome','firefox','msedge');foreach($n in $p){Stop-Process -Name $n -Force -EA SilentlyContinue};Stop-Service 'CCleaner_service' -Force -EA SilentlyContinue;Stop-Service 'SysMain' -Force -EA SilentlyContinue;$gp='HKLM:\SOFTWARE\Microsoft\Windows NT\CurrentVersion\Multimedia\SystemProfile\Tasks\Games';Set-ItemProperty $gp 'GPU Priority' 8 -EA SilentlyContinue;Set-ItemProperty $gp 'Priority' 6 -EA SilentlyContinue;[GC]::Collect()"
            RefreshRAM
            SetStatus "Gaming listo -- Cerrado: Chrome, Warp, Dropbox, OneDrive<br>Prioridad GPU aumentada. Lanza tu juego."
        End Sub

        Sub Restore()
            SetStatus "Restaurando servicios..."
            RunPS "Start-Service 'SysMain' -EA SilentlyContinue"
            If highPerfActive Then
                RunPS "powercfg /setactive SCHEME_BALANCED"
                highPerfActive = False
                document.getElementById("powerLabel").innerHTML = "Perfil actual: Equilibrado"
            End If
            RefreshRAM
            SetStatus "Restaurado -- SysMain reactivado, perfil de energia Equilibrado."
        End Sub

        Sub CleanTemp()
            SetStatus "Limpiando archivos temporales y papelera..."
            RunPS "$dirs=@($env:TEMP,'C:\Windows\Temp');foreach($d in $dirs){Get-ChildItem $d -Recurse -Force -EA SilentlyContinue|Remove-Item -Recurse -Force -EA SilentlyContinue};Clear-RecycleBin -Force -EA SilentlyContinue;[GC]::Collect()"
            RefreshRAM
            SetStatus "Limpieza completada -- %TEMP%, C:\Windows\Temp y papelera vaciados."
        End Sub

        Sub FlushDNS()
            SetStatus "Limpiando cache DNS..."
            RunPS "ipconfig /flushdns | Out-Null; netsh winsock reset catalog | Out-Null"
            SetStatus "DNS limpiado -- Cache DNS y Winsock reiniciados. Util contra lag de conexion."
        End Sub

        Sub TogglePower()
            If highPerfActive Then
                RunPS "powercfg /setactive SCHEME_BALANCED"
                highPerfActive = False
                document.getElementById("powerLabel").innerHTML = "Perfil actual: Equilibrado"
                SetStatus "Perfil cambiado a Equilibrado."
            Else
                RunPS "powercfg /setactive SCHEME_MIN"
                highPerfActive = True
                document.getElementById("powerLabel").innerHTML = "Perfil actual: ALTO RENDIMIENTO"
                SetStatus "Perfil cambiado a Alto Rendimiento -- Ideal para gaming y streaming."
            End If
        End Sub

        Sub UpdateApps()
            SetStatus "Abriendo actualizaciones con winget... (puede tardar varios minutos)"
            WshShell.Run "cmd /c start winget upgrade --all --silent --accept-source-agreements --accept-package-agreements", 1, False
            SetStatus "Actualizaciones en curso -- Se abrio una ventana. Cierra cuando termine."
        End Sub

        Sub ShowContext()
            document.getElementById("overlay").style.display = "block"
        End Sub
        Sub CloseModal()
            document.getElementById("overlay").style.display = "none"
        End Sub
        Sub CopyContext()
            Dim tmp, f, txt
            txt = document.getElementById("ctxArea").value
            tmp = WshShell.ExpandEnvironmentStrings("%TEMP%\ctx_copy.txt")
            Set f = FSO.CreateTextFile(tmp, True, True)
            f.Write txt
            f.Close
            WshShell.Run "cmd /c clip < """ & tmp & """", 0, True
            FSO.DeleteFile tmp
            document.getElementById("copyBtn").innerHTML = "Copiado!"
        End Sub

        Sub Window_OnLoad()
            RefreshRAM
        End Sub

    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Panel de Optimizacion</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Prepara tu PC para streaming o gaming</p>

    <div class="rambar-wrap">
        <div class="rambar-label">
            <span id="ramText">Calculando RAM...</span>
            <span style="color:#444;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer" onclick="RefreshRAM()">Actualizar</span>
        </div>
        <div class="rambar-track">
            <div class="rambar-fill" id="ramFill" style="width:0%"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">Optimizar</div>

    <button class="btn btn-streaming" onclick="OptimizeStreaming()">
        Optimizar para STREAMING
        <div class="desc">Cierra Dropbox, Discord, Steam, Warp, OneDrive, Spotify. Listo para OBS + Twitch.</div>
    </button>

    <button class="btn btn-gaming" onclick="OptimizeGaming()">
        Optimizar para GAMING
        <div class="desc">Cierra Chrome y navegadores. Sube prioridad GPU. Desactiva SysMain.</div>
    </button>

    <button class="btn btn-restore" onclick="Restore()">
        Restaurar servicios
        <div class="desc">Reactiva SysMain y vuelve al perfil de energia Equilibrado.</div>
    </button>

    <div class="section">Herramientas</div>

    <div class="row">
        <button class="btn btn-clean" onclick="CleanTemp()">
            Limpiar temporales
            <div class="desc">Vacia %TEMP% y papelera.</div>
        </button>
        <button class="btn btn-dns" onclick="FlushDNS()">
            Flush DNS
            <div class="desc">Limpia cache DNS y Winsock.</div>
        </button>
    </div>

    <button class="btn btn-power" onclick="TogglePower()">
        Alternar perfil de energia
        <div id="powerLabel" class="desc">Perfil actual: Equilibrado</div>
    </button>

    <button class="btn btn-update" onclick="UpdateApps()">
        Actualizar aplicaciones (winget)
        <div class="desc">Actualiza Chrome, OBS, Discord y demas apps instaladas.</div>
    </button>

    <div class="section">Copilot</div>
    <button class="btn btn-context" onclick="ShowContext()">
        Contexto del proyecto
        <div class="desc">Copia el prompt para continuar en una nueva conversacion.</div>
    </button>

    <div class="status">
        <div class="status-label">Estado</div>
        <div id="statusText">Listo. Selecciona una opcion.</div>
    </div>

    <div id="overlay">
        <div class="modal">
            <h2>Contexto del Proyecto</h2>
            <textarea id="ctxArea" readonly>CONTEXTO DEL PROYECTO: Panel de Optimizacion de PC

Tengo un archivo HTA en mi escritorio llamado "OptimizerPanel.hta".
Panel de control con estos botones:

1. STREAMING: Cierra Dropbox, Warp, Steam, Discord, CCleaner, SearchApp,
   RemoteMouse, OneDrive, Spotify, EpicGames.

2. GAMING: Cierra Chrome, Warp, Dropbox, navegadores.
   Aumenta prioridad GPU. Desactiva SysMain.

3. RESTAURAR: Reactiva SysMain, vuelve a perfil Equilibrado.

4. LIMPIAR TEMPORALES: Vacia %TEMP%, C:\Windows\Temp y papelera.

5. FLUSH DNS: Limpia cache DNS y Winsock.

6. ALTERNAR PERFIL DE ENERGIA: Cambia entre Equilibrado y Alto Rendimiento.

7. ACTUALIZAR APPS: winget upgrade --all

MI SETUP:
- Windows 10/11
- CPU: Intel i5-3470 @ 3.20GHz
- GPU: NVIDIA GTX 1650
- RAM: 15.5 GB
- OBS para streaming a Twitch
- Logitech (LogiOptions activo, LogiBolt desactivado)
- Audio Realtek (no cerrar)

INICIO DESACTIVADO:
- LogiBolt, Java Update Scheduler, iCloud, NVIDIA Overlay

QUIERO: [describe aqui lo que quieres anadir o modificar]</textarea>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button class="mbtn mbtn-copy" id="copyBtn" onclick="CopyContext()">Copiar</button>
                <button class="mbtn mbtn-close" onclick="CloseModal()">Cerrar</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
